---
title: Creamy Chicken Pesto Pasta with Roasted Tomatoes
description: A customer favourite, this Creamy Chicken Pesto Pasta is a tried-and-tested recipe that always wins with a crowd.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R340_W09_UK_C10743-18215-10_Main_low-6ddb6d34.jpg
